<h3>TIE Corps </h3>
<p>The elite of the elite and last line of defense against the spreading chaos. A branch of the Emperor's Hammer that is composed of selected TIE Fighter pilots, battling any threat through Multi-Player competition, custom-made missions and battles. Although all pilots must first meet the entrance requirements, they serve the Emperor's Hammer Strike Fleet as the most elite and highly trained starfighter pilots in the Outer Rim Territories.</p>

<p>The TIE Corps offers an enormous Mission Compendium holding over 4,000 custom missions for all gaming platforms. Multi-Player competitions (X-Wing vs. TIE Fighter, Balance of Power, X-Wing  Alliance) are held regularly for pilots with the courage to fly in them.</p>
Game platforms:
<ul>
